# DOS local secrets — the SHAPE only. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in.
#
# The kernel itself needs NO secrets (PyYAML-only core). These are for OPTIONAL
# out-of-kernel drivers/adjudicators that name a vendor as code — each lives behind
# its own packaging extra and reads its token from the environment. A committed
# token is the exact supply-chain hazard SECURITY.md warns about: keep VALUES local.

# The JUDGE rung's Gemini-backed adjudicator (drivers/llm_judge, the `dos.judges`
# seam). Advisory, fail-to-abstain — absent key ⇒ the judge ABSTAINS, never blocks.
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# The notification spine's Slack transport (drivers/notify_slack, the `[notify-slack]`
# extra, `dos.notifiers`). Absent ⇒ the default `null` sink renders only.
SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=
